PWA - App Manifest
-----
For PWA to behave like native app, must mimic function and view.
Splash screens, icons, etc.
Make app as indistinguishable as possible to web apps.

Must have meta name viewport content width scaling in index.html.

Manifest gives devs the ability to control how the app appears in situations.

Create-react app generates a favicon, but don't have all other sized icons for various devices.
favicon generator to create icons for everything.
Also will give a splash screen that's shown during loading.